797
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:43,820
 Da, da.

798
00:42:43,820 --> 00:42:44,520
 Da krećete iz početka.

799
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:46,080
 Ali to je i cijeli naš narod.

800
00:42:46,080 --> 00:42:47,180
 Ali to je nova generacija,

