 Dakle, to je sve skupa prolazno

822
00:43:28,980 --> 00:43:31,360
 i ja to me ne bih predavao preveliku pažnju.

823
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:34,080
 Ja bi više htio reći nešto drugo,

824
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:35,400
 što se danas radi,

825
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:37,840
 danas se sustavno radi,

826
00:43:37,840 --> 00:43:40,320
 ja bih to nazvao historiocid.

827
00:43:40,320 --> 00:43:42,540
 Ne znam jel ta riječ uopće postoji

828
00:43:42,540 --> 00:43:43,660
 u političkom riječniku,

829
00:43:43,660 --> 00:43:44,800
 ja nisam našao nigdje.

830
00:43:44,800 --> 00:43:47,160
 Vjerojatno, zato jer to još niko do sad nije

831
00:43:47,160 --> 00:43:49,380
 se usudio nikome napraviti.

832
00:43:49,380 --> 00:43:52,420
 Ali danas se nama Hrvatima radi baš to,

833
00:43:52,420 --> 00:43:54,280
 uništenje naše povijesti.

834
00:43:54,280 --> 00:43:57,520
 Dakle, ne samo one davne povijesti,

835
00:43:57,620 --> 00:43:59,260
 nego i ove vidjeli smo u dvoru na Uni,

836
00:43:59,260 --> 00:44:01,520
 ali i druge povijesti.

837
00:44:01,520 --> 00:44:05,060
 Tako da, čujem recimo da je

838
00:44:05,060 --> 00:44:06,960
 srpski političar,

839
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:07,860
 da ga ne imenujem,

840
00:44:07,860 --> 00:44:08,840
 neću ga reklamirat,

841
00:44:08,840 --> 00:44:11,720
 rekao da Nikola Tesla

842
00:44:11,720 --> 00:44:13,480
 nikad nije stupio na tlo Hrvatske.

843
00:44:13,480 --> 00:44:15,940
 Drugim riječima da Hrvatske

844
00:44:15,940 --> 00:44:17,740
 nije bilo u doba njegovog rođenja

845
00:44:17,740 --> 00:44:19,280
 i djetnjstva i rane mladosti.

846
00:44:19,860 --> 00:44:21,200
 I to je vrlo opaka,

847
00:44:21,200 --> 00:44:23,480
 smišljena podvala, jel?

848
00:44:23,480 --> 00:44:25,440
 Nije bilo jer je bila Austro-Ugarska.

849
00:44:25,440 --> 00:44:26,960
 Da, ali se je to zvalo

850
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:28,700
 Hrvatska vojna granica,

851
00:44:28,700 --> 00:44:30,460
 Kroatiše militer granice,

852
00:44:30,460 --> 00:44:31,660
 tako se je to zvalo

853
00:44:31,660 --> 00:44:33,560
 i kasnije je vraćena pod vlast

854
00:44:33,560 --> 00:44:34,920
 bana i sabora.

855
00:44:34,920 --> 00:44:36,700
 Dakle, to se zanemaruje.

856
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:39,700
 Ali to je fakt istava ona propaganda

857
00:44:39,700 --> 00:44:41,380
 koju smo mi za vrijeme Jugoslavije

858
00:44:41,380 --> 00:44:43,300
 morali učiti u školama

859
00:44:43,300 --> 00:44:44,220
 koje su oni širili,

860
00:44:44,220 --> 00:44:44,840
 to je za to.

861
00:44:44,840 --> 00:44:45,460
 Ali gore.

862
00:44:45,460 --> 00:44:46,780
 Još gore, slažem se.

863
00:44:46,780 --> 00:44:48,400
 Jer mi smo u školi učili

864
00:44:48,400 --> 00:44:49,780
 da je postojala Hrvatska

865
00:44:49,780 --> 00:44:51,880
 unutar usprezisa Mađarska

866
00:44:51,880 --> 00:44:53,660
 i sa Austrijom

867
00:44:53,660 --> 00:44:55,620
 i da su postoje Libanovi

868
00:44:55,620 --> 00:44:56,220
 i lijevo-desno.

869
00:44:56,220 --> 00:44:56,920
 Učilo se je nešto.

870
00:44:56,920 --> 00:44:57,960
 Tako je, slažem se.

871
00:44:57,960 --> 00:45:01,340
 Ali u Beogradu se sada govori

872
00:45:01,340 --> 00:45:02,660
 da nema Hrvatske

873
00:45:02,660 --> 00:45:08,140
 i da se onda posižu

874
00:45:08,140 --> 00:45:10,140
 za našim velikim umovima.

875
00:45:10,140 --> 00:45:11,480
 Naravno, Nikola Tesla je tu

876
00:45:11,480 --> 00:45:12,200
 na prvom mjestu

877
00:45:12,200 --> 00:45:13,560
 gdje bi oni htili da bude Srbin,

878
00:45:13,560 --> 00:45:14,900
 ali to je priča za sebe.

879
00:45:14,900 --> 00:45:16,640
 Teško je to ubaciti

880
00:45:16,640 --> 00:45:17,600
 u ovakav razgovor.

881
00:45:17,600 --> 00:45:19,860
 Ali onda i Ruđira Boškovića

882
00:45:19,860 --> 00:45:20,740
 i Ivana Gundulića

883
00:45:20,740 --> 00:45:21,400
 i da ne govorim

884
00:45:21,400 --> 00:45:22,400
 ko sve dalje,

885
00:45:22,400 --> 00:45:24,020
 ali ne samo njih,

886
00:45:24,020 --> 00:45:25,300
 nego i moderne,

887
00:45:25,300 --> 00:45:26,400
 najnovije,

888
00:45:26,400 --> 00:45:28,280
 ne samo Hrvate,

889
00:45:28,280 --> 00:45:29,180
 nego i Slovence.

890
00:45:29,180 --> 00:45:30,880
 Ja sam našao članak

891
00:45:30,880 --> 00:45:32,700
 u jednom pjevaču,

892
00:45:32,700 --> 00:45:33,820
 neću ga sad spomenuti,

893
00:45:33,820 --> 00:45:34,600
 jer kožda,

894
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:35,880
 možda on ne bi htio

895
00:45:35,880 --> 00:45:36,580
 da ga se spomene,

896
00:45:36,580 --> 00:45:39,440
 koji je zagrebački,

897
00:45:39,440 --> 00:45:42,360
 u biti ljubljanski rođeni slovenac,

898
00:45:42,360 --> 00:45:43,800
 koji pjevao u Zagrebu,

899
00:45:43,800 --> 00:45:46,480
 a živio je 15 godina u Srbiji

900
00:45:46,480 --> 00:45:47,840
 jer je bio ženjen za srpkinju.

901
00:45:47,840 --> 00:45:48,760
 I oni kažu,

902
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:49,680
 srpski pevač

903
00:45:49,680 --> 00:45:50,600
 koji živi u Ljubljani.

904
00:45:50,600 --> 00:45:52,300
 Pa onda,

905
00:45:52,300 --> 00:45:54,500
 košarkaša,

906
00:45:54,500 --> 00:45:56,060
 koji je bio legenda Hrvatske,

907
00:45:56,060 --> 00:45:57,480
 oni proglašavaju

908
00:45:57,480 --> 00:45:58,540
 srpskom legendom.

909
00:45:59,540 --> 00:46:01,800
 legenda jugoslavijanske košarke,

910
00:46:01,800 --> 00:46:02,000
 jel?

911
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:02,940
 Slovenac.

912
00:46:02,940 --> 00:46:04,220
 Oni kažu,

913
00:46:04,220 --> 00:46:05,180
 srpska legenda.

914
00:46:05,180 --> 00:46:05,820
 Dakle,

915
00:46:05,820 --> 00:46:08,020
 sve to polako ide redom,

916
00:46:08,020 --> 00:46:09,580
 a vrhunac svega je

917
00:46:09,580 --> 00:46:10,480
 2010.

918
00:46:10,480 --> 00:46:12,000
 koje je,

919
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,360
 kada je ispod radara prošlo,

920
00:46:13,360 --> 00:46:14,420
 bilo je u novinama,

921
00:46:14,420 --> 00:46:15,440
 ali nisam čuo

922
00:46:15,440 --> 00:46:15,960
 da je njegov

923
00:46:15,960 --> 00:46:17,920
 baš puno primijetio,

924
00:46:17,920 --> 00:46:19,320
 kada je srpski

925
00:46:19,320 --> 00:46:21,700
 olimpijski odbor,

926
00:46:22,400 --> 00:46:23,700
 sve medalje Jugoslavije

927
00:46:23,700 --> 00:46:24,480
 i prve i druge

928
00:46:24,480 --> 00:46:25,960
 pripisao srbiji.

929
00:46:25,960 --> 00:46:27,460
 Pa su tako srbi postali

930
00:46:27,460 --> 00:46:28,400
 i Leon Štukalj,

931
00:46:28,400 --> 00:46:29,260
 i Miroslav Cerar,

932
00:46:29,260 --> 00:46:30,620
 i Đuždica Bjedov,

933
00:46:30,620 --> 00:46:32,100
 i Četverac Gusara,

934
00:46:32,100 --> 00:46:33,600
 i Mateo Parlov,

935
00:46:33,600 --> 00:46:34,580
 i Dan Brankosve.

936
00:46:34,580 --> 00:46:35,240
 onda ste i vi,

937
00:46:35,240 --> 00:46:36,040
 u stvari, isto.

938
00:46:36,040 --> 00:46:36,860
 Ne, ne.

939
00:46:36,860 --> 00:46:37,640
 Uklapate,

940
00:46:37,640 --> 00:46:40,080
 kao junior 68. godine.

941
00:46:40,080 --> 00:46:40,980
 Nisam olimpijac.

942
00:46:40,980 --> 00:46:42,360
 Da, niste olimpijac,

943
00:46:42,360 --> 00:46:43,940
 ali vi ste onda taj njihov sportač.

944
00:46:43,940 --> 00:46:45,040
 Nisam dovoljno važan.

945
00:46:45,040 --> 00:46:46,220
 Još nisu došli do toga.

946
00:46:46,220 --> 00:46:47,280
 Nisam dovoljno važan

947
00:46:47,280 --> 00:46:48,160
 da postanem srbin.

948
00:46:48,160 --> 00:46:49,120
 Ali,

949
00:46:49,120 --> 00:46:51,700
 taj način

950
00:46:51,700 --> 00:46:53,160
 da se prigrabi

951
00:46:53,160 --> 00:46:54,220
 sve što je tuđa,

952
00:46:54,220 --> 00:46:55,260
 pogotovo Hrvatsko,

953
00:46:55,260 --> 00:46:56,980
 to je sada postalo

954
00:46:56,980 --> 00:46:58,320
 toliko bezobzirno

955
00:46:58,320 --> 00:46:59,560
 i bez granica.

956
00:46:59,560 --> 00:47:01,580
 Nažalost,

957
00:47:01,580 --> 00:47:02,760
 na ruku im idu

958
00:47:02,760 --> 00:47:03,960
 neki potvizi

959
00:47:03,960 --> 00:47:05,060
 koje mi sami radimo.

960
00:47:05,060 --> 00:47:06,140
 Odnosno vlast Hrvatska.

961
00:47:06,140 --> 00:47:06,960
 A ja bih sve htio

962
00:47:06,960 --> 00:47:08,340
 javno reći jednu stvar

963
00:47:08,340 --> 00:47:09,740
 koja se događa u ulici.

964
00:47:09,740 --> 00:47:11,120
 U ulici je

965
00:47:11,120 --> 00:47:12,720
 u planu

966
00:47:12,720 --> 00:47:14,880
 i već su svi pripreme,

967
00:47:14,880 --> 00:47:15,700
 su sve gotove

968
00:47:15,700 --> 00:47:16,420
 i zapravo

969
00:47:16,420 --> 00:47:18,120
 posao je počeo.

970
00:47:18,120 --> 00:47:19,940
 Izgradnja hidrocentrale

971
00:47:19,940 --> 00:47:20,440
 Sejm-2.

972
00:47:20,440 --> 00:47:22,180
 Sejm-2 to je

973
00:47:22,180 --> 00:47:23,100
 veliki projekt,

974
00:47:23,100 --> 00:47:24,380
 to je 400 megawata

975
00:47:24,380 --> 00:47:24,880
 centrala,

976
00:47:24,880 --> 00:47:25,800
 dakle,

977
00:47:25,800 --> 00:47:27,300
 više od pola nuklearke,

978
00:47:27,300 --> 00:47:28,260
 ajmo reći,

979
00:47:28,260 --> 00:47:29,120
 u Krškom.

980
00:47:29,120 --> 00:47:29,420
 Dakle,

981
00:47:29,420 --> 00:47:31,500
 više nego cijeli

982
00:47:31,500 --> 00:47:33,140
 hrvatski dio nuklearke Krškom.

983
00:47:33,340 --> 00:47:34,100
 Dakle,

984
00:47:34,100 --> 00:47:34,780
 velik projekt.

985
00:47:34,780 --> 00:47:35,720
 Međutim,

986
00:47:35,720 --> 00:47:37,260
 da bi se taj projekt napravio,

987
00:47:37,260 --> 00:47:38,220
 treba potopiti

988
00:47:38,220 --> 00:47:38,780
 velik dio

989
00:47:38,780 --> 00:47:39,700
 Košinske doline.

990
00:47:39,700 --> 00:47:40,840
 Sad,

991
00:47:40,840 --> 00:47:41,700
 Košinska dolina

992
00:47:41,700 --> 00:47:42,520
 nije bilo što.

993
00:47:42,520 --> 00:47:43,440
 To je,

994
00:47:43,440 --> 00:47:45,020
 mjesto Košinjca,

995
00:47:45,020 --> 00:47:45,620
 okolicom,

996
00:47:45,620 --> 00:47:46,540
 je bio centar

997
00:47:46,540 --> 00:47:48,080
 knezova Košinskih,

998
00:47:48,080 --> 00:47:49,380
 koji su kasnije

999
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:50,100
 se zamijenili

1000
00:47:50,100 --> 00:47:51,120
 sa Frankopanima,

1001
00:47:51,120 --> 00:47:52,300
 pa je Ivan Anž,

1002
00:47:52,300 --> 00:47:53,780
 osmi Frankopan,

1003
00:47:53,780 --> 00:47:54,480
 Brinski,

1004
00:47:54,480 --> 00:47:56,160
 jer ima i onaj na Krku,

1005
00:47:56,160 --> 00:47:56,740
 Dakle,

1006
00:47:56,740 --> 00:47:57,160
 Brinski,

1007
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:59,140
 tamo stolovao

1008
00:47:59,140 --> 00:48:00,680
 i njegov dvorac,

1009
00:48:00,680 --> 00:48:01,440
 bivši,

1010
00:48:01,440 --> 00:48:02,220
 koji je srušen

1011
00:48:02,220 --> 00:48:03,220
 danas ga nema više,

1012
00:48:03,220 --> 00:48:04,480
 je,

1013
00:48:04,480 --> 00:48:05,220
 hvala Bogu,

1014
00:48:05,220 --> 00:48:06,420
 mjesto gde je on bio

1015
00:48:06,420 --> 00:48:07,420
 neće biti potopljenu.

1016
00:48:07,420 --> 00:48:08,200
 Za nijansu,

1017
00:48:08,200 --> 00:48:09,940
 za zadlaku neće biti potopljenu.

1018
00:48:10,600 --> 00:48:13,540
 Tamo je bila prva hrvatska štamparija

1019
00:48:13,540 --> 00:48:17,100
 i tamo su od štampane neke od Inkunabula,

1020
00:48:17,100 --> 00:48:17,440
 dakle,

1021
00:48:17,440 --> 00:48:21,020
 knjiga tiskanih prije 1500. godine,

1022
00:48:21,020 --> 00:48:22,560
 svjetski raritet,

1023
00:48:22,560 --> 00:48:28,660
 a unutar toga ima preko 30 arheoloških nalazišta,

1024
00:48:28,660 --> 00:48:31,360
 a gotovo svaka kuća je spomeni kulture.

1025
00:48:31,360 --> 00:48:33,600
 I sve to dolazi pod vodom.

1026
00:48:33,600 --> 00:48:37,700
 Dobro, vlada je ove godine dala

1027
00:48:37,700 --> 00:48:40,180
 svoju suglasnost da je to vladin

1028
00:48:40,180 --> 00:48:41,600
 strateški projekt.

1029
00:48:41,600 --> 00:48:43,380
 Dakle, vlada od toga neće odustat

1030
00:48:43,380 --> 00:48:46,640
 i sad više nema se šta odustat,

1031
00:48:46,640 --> 00:48:47,320
 sad je gotovo.

1032
00:48:47,320 --> 00:48:51,740
 Međutim, postoji zakonska obveza vlade

1033
00:48:51,740 --> 00:48:54,440
 da se ne potapa prije,

1034
00:48:54,440 --> 00:48:56,980
 nego se istraže sva arheološka nalazišta.

1035
00:48:56,980 --> 00:48:59,140
 Ja još uvijek nisam primijetio

1036
00:48:59,140 --> 00:49:01,100
 da je i ko i gdje kramp zabutamo.

1037
00:49:01,100 --> 00:49:03,500
 I što će se kasnije dogoditi,

1038
00:49:03,500 --> 00:49:04,920
 na koji način će oni to riješiti,

1039
00:49:04,920 --> 00:49:05,420
 ja ne znam,

1040
00:49:05,420 --> 00:49:07,160
 ali o tome niko ne brine.

1041
00:49:07,160 --> 00:49:09,280
 Ali ja nisam iznenađena,

1042
00:49:09,280 --> 00:49:13,300
 zašto bi bili iznenađeni time

1043
00:49:13,300 --> 00:49:16,040
 da se ne brinu o arheološkim nalazištima,

1044
00:49:16,040 --> 00:49:17,980
 ako se tako malo brinu

1045
00:49:17,980 --> 00:49:20,360
 o širenju istine domovinskom ratu.

1046
00:49:20,360 --> 00:49:20,640
 Da, jesno.

1047
00:49:20,640 --> 00:49:21,000
 Zašto?

1048
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:22,480
 Ako nešto što se dogodilo

1049
00:49:22,480 --> 00:49:24,760
 prije 30 godina,

1050
00:49:24,760 --> 00:49:25,380
 nešto što je,

1051
00:49:25,380 --> 00:49:27,840
 što postoje živi svjedoci,

1052
00:49:27,840 --> 00:49:29,760
 imamo ministra branitelja

1053
00:49:29,760 --> 00:49:30,880
 koji je bio branitelj,

1054
00:49:30,880 --> 00:49:33,540
 dakle, spomenuli ste gospodina Medveda,

1055
00:49:33,540 --> 00:49:35,280
 dakle, imamo ljude koji su,

1056
00:49:35,860 --> 00:49:36,960
 imaju sad je premijer,

1057
00:49:36,960 --> 00:49:38,640
 zato što je neko dao svoj život,

1058
00:49:38,640 --> 00:49:39,340
 ovaj mladić,

1059
00:49:39,340 --> 00:49:40,780
 koji je kraj vas poginuo,

1060
00:49:40,780 --> 00:49:42,880
 ako oni se ne bave,

1061
00:49:42,880 --> 00:49:44,960
 a ne bave se dovoljno,

1062
00:49:44,960 --> 00:49:47,140
 zaštitom istine o domovinskom ratu,

1063
00:49:47,140 --> 00:49:48,500
 zašto bi onda,

1064
00:49:48,500 --> 00:49:50,940
 kako bi očekivali od njih da će štititi istinu

1065
00:49:50,940 --> 00:49:52,700
 o povijesti Hrvatskoj.

1066
00:49:52,700 --> 00:49:55,380
 Da, ali se zanemaruje istina

1067
00:49:55,380 --> 00:49:58,200
 o ljudima koji su zaslužni

1068
00:49:58,200 --> 00:49:59,020
 da uopće imamo,

1069
00:49:59,020 --> 00:50:01,360
 mi ne bi imali ništa za obraniti,

1070
00:50:01,360 --> 00:50:04,080
 nijedan centimetar Hrvatske 91-ve,

1071
00:50:04,080 --> 00:50:06,700
 da nije bilo onih ispred nas,

1072
00:50:06,700 --> 00:50:08,540
 onih koji su davno prije bili.

1073
00:50:08,540 --> 00:50:09,680
 Evo, na primjer,

1074
00:50:09,680 --> 00:50:12,240
 ja ću vam spomenuti 22. lipanj,

1075
00:50:12,280 --> 00:50:14,960
 kad partizani tamo slave

1076
00:50:14,960 --> 00:50:17,540
 neki odred kojeg tamo

1077
00:50:17,540 --> 00:50:18,720
 uopće nije bilo u to doba.

1078
00:50:18,720 --> 00:50:20,940
 Evo, i to je danas dokazano,

1079
00:50:20,940 --> 00:50:22,580
 jasno, ali uporno dalje se

1080
00:50:22,580 --> 00:50:23,880
 ta istina negira.

1081
00:50:23,880 --> 00:50:26,020
 Ali, to čak nije ni najgore,

1082
00:50:26,020 --> 00:50:27,260
 pa niko oni svoje slave.

1083
00:50:27,260 --> 00:50:29,900
 Ali mi sami,

1084
00:50:29,900 --> 00:50:31,620
 i vjernici, i svečenstvo,

1085
00:50:31,620 --> 00:50:34,820
 dakle ljudi koji su doista pozitivci,

1086
00:50:34,820 --> 00:50:38,400
 ne uzimamo u obzir

1087
00:50:38,400 --> 00:50:40,500
 da je tamo na taj isti dan,

1088
00:50:41,100 --> 00:50:42,980
 ali nekoliko stotina godine ranije,

1089
00:50:42,980 --> 00:50:44,160
 1593.

1090
00:50:44,160 --> 00:50:46,600
 Bila najjača,

1091
00:50:46,600 --> 00:50:48,520
 najveća hrvatska pobjeda

1092
00:50:48,520 --> 00:50:49,920
 protiv Turaka u povijesti.

1093
00:50:49,920 --> 00:50:51,560
 Strateška pobjeda

1094
00:50:51,560 --> 00:50:53,860
 koja je preokrenula tijek rata.

1095
00:50:53,860 --> 00:50:55,720
 Do tada su Turci bili

1096
00:50:55,720 --> 00:50:57,160
 u napadnim akcijama,

1097
00:50:57,160 --> 00:50:58,520
 nakon toga su bili

1098
00:50:58,520 --> 00:50:59,380
 u obrambenim.

1099
00:50:59,380 --> 00:51:00,640
 Inicijativa prelazija

1100
00:51:00,640 --> 00:51:01,600
 na stranu Hrvatske,

1101
00:51:01,600 --> 00:51:03,220
 odnosno Austrije,

1102
00:51:03,220 --> 00:51:05,260
 s kojima je tada Hrvatska bila zajedno.

1103
00:51:05,260 --> 00:51:06,700
 I ta pobjeda

1104
00:51:06,700 --> 00:51:09,340
 na Turcima se uopće ne obilježava

1105
00:51:09,340 --> 00:51:10,340
 i ne samo to.

1106
00:51:10,340 --> 00:51:12,680
 Ja sam 22. lipnje

1107
00:51:12,680 --> 00:51:13,100
 ove godine

1108
00:51:13,100 --> 00:51:14,660
 došao namjerno u Sisak,

1109
00:51:14,660 --> 00:51:16,000
 kraj tvojeg dvorca,

1110
00:51:16,000 --> 00:51:16,780
 stare tvrđave,

1111
00:51:16,780 --> 00:51:18,280
 i pitao konobara

1112
00:51:18,280 --> 00:51:19,300
 koji bi jedino živo

1113
00:51:19,300 --> 00:51:20,540
 ljudsko biće tamo,

1114
00:51:20,540 --> 00:51:23,340
 oće li biti kakva obilježavanja?

1115
00:51:23,340 --> 00:51:23,820
 Kaže,

1116
00:51:23,820 --> 00:51:25,100
 neće biti zbog korone,

1117
00:51:25,100 --> 00:51:26,540
 ali partizani su

1118
00:51:26,540 --> 00:51:27,900
 bez obzira na koronu došli.

1119
00:51:27,900 --> 00:51:29,160
 Nije bilo ničega,

1120
00:51:29,160 --> 00:51:29,520
 ja kažem,

1121
00:51:29,520 --> 00:51:31,500
 postoji li nekakva spomen ploča?

1122
00:51:31,500 --> 00:51:32,020
 Bilo što,

1123
00:51:32,020 --> 00:51:33,460
 makar ovakva mala pločica

1124
00:51:33,460 --> 00:51:35,100
 da piše što se je dogodilo

1125
00:51:35,100 --> 00:51:36,740
 prije 400 godina,

1126
00:51:36,740 --> 00:51:37,740
 kaže,

1127
00:51:37,740 --> 00:51:38,860
 ne znam,

1128
00:51:38,860 --> 00:51:40,020
 ima samo ono tamo.

1129
00:51:40,020 --> 00:51:40,880
 Ja pogledam,

1130
00:51:40,880 --> 00:51:43,000
 to je bilo nešto drveno,

1131
00:51:43,000 --> 00:51:43,880
 nalikne raspelo,

1132
00:51:43,880 --> 00:51:45,080
 ali nije raspelo,

1133
00:51:45,080 --> 00:51:46,100
 nego drveni pano,

1134
00:51:46,100 --> 00:51:47,340
 na kojem je pisalo

1135
00:51:47,340 --> 00:51:48,520
 što u Sisku ima,

1136
00:51:48,520 --> 00:51:49,000
 gdje,

1137
00:51:49,140 --> 00:51:49,700
 koji je hotel,

1138
00:51:49,700 --> 00:51:50,480
 restauracija,

1139
00:51:50,480 --> 00:51:51,460
 brijačnica i to.

1140
00:51:51,460 --> 00:51:52,220
 Dakle,

1141
00:51:52,220 --> 00:51:54,300
 ništa nema spomena

1142
00:51:54,300 --> 00:51:54,860
 o tome

1143
00:51:54,860 --> 00:51:56,460
 što su učinili ljudi

1144
00:51:56,460 --> 00:51:57,280
 koji su tada

1145
00:51:57,280 --> 00:51:58,380
 spasili Hrvatsku,

1146
00:51:58,380 --> 00:51:59,980
 jer da su tu bitku izgubili,

1147
00:51:59,980 --> 00:52:01,080
 sljedeći je na redu

1148
00:52:01,080 --> 00:52:01,900
 bi bio Zagreb,

1149
00:52:01,900 --> 00:52:03,240
 nakon toga Grac,

1150
00:52:03,240 --> 00:52:05,180
 a nakon Graca

1151
00:52:05,180 --> 00:52:06,680
 se Beć ne bi moglo spasiti.

1152
00:52:06,680 --> 00:52:07,980
 E to su sve,

1153
00:52:07,980 --> 00:52:08,780
 to su stvari

1154
00:52:08,780 --> 00:52:09,720
 koje moramo znati

1155
00:52:09,720 --> 00:52:10,340
 iz povijesti,

1156
00:52:10,340 --> 00:52:11,700
 ne zbog povijesti,

1157
00:52:11,700 --> 00:52:12,980
 nego zato jer moramo

1158
00:52:12,980 --> 00:52:13,520
 biti svjesni

1159
00:52:13,520 --> 00:52:14,980
 da danas ne bismo imali

1160
00:52:14,980 --> 00:52:16,420
 ništa od Hrvatske,

1161
00:52:16,420 --> 00:52:17,440
 da ti ljudi

1162
00:52:17,440 --> 00:52:18,780
 tamo nisu ginuli.

1163
00:52:18,780 --> 00:52:20,580
 To što ne bi imali ništa

1164
00:52:20,580 --> 00:52:22,120
 da ljudi poput vas

1165
00:52:22,120 --> 00:52:23,980
 nisu bili u obrani Hrvatske

1166
00:52:23,980 --> 00:52:25,080
 i ovih koji su poginuli,

1167
00:52:25,080 --> 00:52:25,900
 da oni nisu poginuli.

1168
00:52:25,900 --> 00:52:26,940
 Slažem se s vama,

1169
00:52:26,940 --> 00:52:28,860
 taj kontinuitet,

1170
00:52:28,860 --> 00:52:30,400
 onda u čovjeku

1171
00:52:30,400 --> 00:52:31,660
 mladom

1172
00:52:31,660 --> 00:52:32,880
 i u svakom drugom

1173
00:52:32,880 --> 00:52:33,700
 potiče ljubav

1174
00:52:33,700 --> 00:52:34,680
 prema svom narodu,

1175
00:52:34,680 --> 00:52:36,120
 divljenje prema svom narodu

1176
00:52:36,120 --> 00:52:36,380
 i ponost.

1177
00:52:36,380 --> 00:52:37,120
 Ali samo svijest.

1178
00:52:37,120 --> 00:52:38,100
 Tako, ponost,

1179
00:52:38,100 --> 00:52:39,020
 da si dio toga.

1180
00:52:39,020 --> 00:52:40,880
 Jer je 1593.

1181
00:52:40,880 --> 00:52:41,860
 je Hrvatska

1182
00:52:41,860 --> 00:52:43,220
 spašena, obranjena,

1183
00:52:43,220 --> 00:52:45,380
 a 1856.

1184
00:52:45,380 --> 00:52:46,520
 kada je Nikola Tesla

1185
00:52:46,520 --> 00:52:47,020
 rođen je

1186
00:52:47,440 --> 00:52:47,880
 bilo.

1187
00:52:47,880 --> 00:52:49,200
 Dakle, to je...

1188
00:52:49,200 --> 00:52:50,620
 Kažu veliko Srbi.

1189
00:52:50,620 --> 00:52:52,100
 To se mora,

1190
00:52:52,100 --> 00:52:54,500
 o tome Hrvati moraju znati,

1191
00:52:54,500 --> 00:52:55,800
 o tome djeca moraju

1192
00:52:55,800 --> 00:52:56,720
 u školi učiti.

1193
00:52:56,720 --> 00:52:58,480
 A djeca ne spominju to.

1194
00:52:58,480 --> 00:52:59,900
 Kad sam ja bio u školi,

1195
00:52:59,900 --> 00:53:01,020
 mi smo učili o

1196
00:53:01,020 --> 00:53:02,200
 Rimskom carstvu,

1197
00:53:02,200 --> 00:53:03,400
 o Punskim ratovima,

1198
00:53:03,400 --> 00:53:05,460
 o Perzijskom carstvu,

1199
00:53:05,460 --> 00:53:06,460
 o Grčkom bogovima,

1200
00:53:06,460 --> 00:53:09,520
 o Grčkim polisima,

1201
00:53:09,520 --> 00:53:10,460
 o Napoleonu,

1202
00:53:10,460 --> 00:53:12,580
 o oktobratskoj revoluciji,

1203
00:53:12,580 --> 00:53:13,240
 o fašizmu,

1204
00:53:13,320 --> 00:53:13,820
 nacizmu,

1205
00:53:13,820 --> 00:53:14,460
 o NUB-u,

1206
00:53:14,460 --> 00:53:15,320
 o svemu,

1207
00:53:15,320 --> 00:53:16,980
 samo ne o hrvatskoj povijesti.

1208
00:53:16,980 --> 00:53:17,920
 Ali ono što je problem

1209
00:53:17,920 --> 00:53:18,800
 je to danas,

1210
00:53:18,800 --> 00:53:20,320
 djeca nedovoljno dobro uče.

1211
00:53:20,320 --> 00:53:21,260
 Tako, to je problem.

1212
00:53:21,260 --> 00:53:23,080
 Evo, puno, puno,

1213
00:53:23,080 --> 00:53:24,760
 naše vrijeme ide prema kraju.

1214
00:53:24,760 --> 00:53:27,580
 Ja bih vam se htjela zahvaliti

1215
00:53:27,580 --> 00:53:28,820
 za sudjelovanje

1216
00:53:28,820 --> 00:53:32,020
 i za vaš stalni angažman

1217
00:53:32,020 --> 00:53:34,220
 oko istine

1218
00:53:34,220 --> 00:53:36,020
 i vaša predstava

1219
00:53:36,020 --> 00:53:36,840
 koju ste postavili.

1220
00:53:36,840 --> 00:53:38,480
 Nažalost, ne možete ju prikazivati.

1221
00:53:38,480 --> 00:53:41,000
 Je odlična.

1222
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:42,880
 Mene je tako i nasmijela

1223
00:53:42,880 --> 00:53:45,200
 ta priča jedna osobna

1224
00:53:45,200 --> 00:53:46,360
 sa odmakom

1225
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:50,260
 samo nekakve i kritike

1226
00:53:50,260 --> 00:53:53,180
 i šale na svoj račun.

1227
00:53:53,180 --> 00:53:55,020
 Evo, tako da, hvala vam.

1228
00:53:55,020 --> 00:53:56,600
 Hvala vam da ste me pozvali

1229
00:53:56,600 --> 00:53:58,120
 i htio bih poručiti svima

1230
00:53:58,120 --> 00:53:59,240
 koji su nas gledali

1231
00:53:59,240 --> 00:54:02,260
 da neka ne budu pesimistični,

1232
00:54:02,260 --> 00:54:03,320
 neka ne budu tužni.

1233
00:54:03,320 --> 00:54:05,040
 Jer sve ovo što vam se zadesilo

1234
00:54:05,040 --> 00:54:07,240
 to je jedna vrsta

1235
00:54:07,240 --> 00:54:09,340
 povijesnog razvoja

1236
00:54:09,340 --> 00:54:11,180
 faza koju moramo proći.

1237
00:54:11,180 --> 00:54:12,540
 Nažalost, moramo proći

1238
00:54:12,540 --> 00:54:13,520
 da bi se pročistili

1239
00:54:13,520 --> 00:54:14,580
 kroz naše glave,

1240
00:54:14,580 --> 00:54:15,320
 kroz naš um,

1241
00:54:15,320 --> 00:54:17,220
 da možemo opće zaslužiti

1242
00:54:17,220 --> 00:54:17,940
 nešto boljeg.

1243
00:54:17,940 --> 00:54:20,020
 U svemu je važno

1244
00:54:20,020 --> 00:54:22,240
 držati hladnu glavu

1245
00:54:22,240 --> 00:54:22,960
 u vruće srce,

1246
00:54:22,960 --> 00:54:23,640
 ne dat se

1247
00:54:23,640 --> 00:54:25,800
 i što je ja meni važno,

1248
00:54:25,800 --> 00:54:27,560
 volio bih da svima bude važno,

1249
00:54:27,560 --> 00:54:28,420
 a to je molitva.

1250
00:54:28,420 --> 00:54:31,520
 Ako vi nemate u sebi vjeru

1251
00:54:31,520 --> 00:54:32,860
 i u vjeru u to

1252
00:54:32,860 --> 00:54:33,620
 da vas netko,

1253
00:54:33,620 --> 00:54:35,780
 da netko stoji kraj vas,

1254
00:54:35,780 --> 00:54:37,620
 da je Isus stano s nama,

1255
00:54:37,620 --> 00:54:40,260
 onda ćete vrlo teško proći

1256
00:54:40,260 --> 00:54:42,200
 kroz zle situacije.

1257
00:54:42,200 --> 00:54:45,260
 Jer sila uvijek ima puno više

1258
00:54:45,260 --> 00:54:46,320
 i oružja i novaca.

1259
00:54:46,320 --> 00:54:48,500
 Ali onaj koji ima duhovnu snagu,

1260
00:54:48,500 --> 00:54:49,540
 taj pobjeđuje.

1261
00:54:49,780 --> 00:54:51,320
 duhovna snaga je pobjeđivala

1262
00:54:51,320 --> 00:54:53,340
 i u srednjem vijeku,

1263
00:54:53,340 --> 00:54:54,940
 a i u domovinskom ratu,

1264
00:54:54,940 --> 00:54:56,100
 pobjeđit će i dalje.

1265
00:54:56,680 --> 00:54:57,500
 Hvala vam puno.

1266
00:54:57,500 --> 00:54:58,880
 Evo, dragi gledatelji,

1267
00:54:58,880 --> 00:55:00,280
 puno vam hvala na pozornosti

1268
00:55:00,280 --> 00:55:01,840
 i pozdravljam vas do sljedećeg.

1269
00:55:01,840 --> 00:55:03,380
 Hvala vam.

1270
00:55:03,380 --> 00:55:03,380
 Hvala vam.

1271
00:55:03,380 --> 00:55:03,840
 Hvala vam.

